---
<section class="section-colored section-primary overflow-hidden relative pt-10" id="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="flex justify-center mb-6">
      <img src="logo2025.png" alt="logo" class="w-full md:w-2/3 lg:w-1/2 h-auto rounded">
    </div>
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl tracking-tight font-normal text-force-gray-700 text-center mt-6 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      Technology Roundtable on the future of Asahikawa <span class="block"
        >for Makers and ENgineers.</span
      >
    </h2>
    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl mt-6 tracking-tight font-normal text-force-gray-800 text-center text-auto-phrase max-w-3xl mx-auto font-kikai">
      上川地方に技術の知見を惜しみなく注ぐ，技術好きのための円卓会議
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section-colored section-light overflow-hidden relative" id="abstract">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="text-center mb-8">
      <span class="title-plate title-plate-xl">About</span>
    </h2>
    <div class="card control-panel control-panel-screw-enhanced p-8 md:p-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="bottom-screw-left"></div>
      <div class="bottom-screw-right"></div>
      
      <!-- Status LED Panel -->
      <div class="led-panel mb-6 flex justify-between items-center">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <div class="led-indicator led-sm led-green led-pulse"></div>
          <span class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-600">SYSTEM ONLINE</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <div class="led-indicator led-sm led-blue"></div>
          <span class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-600">CONFERENCE</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <div class="led-indicator led-sm led-yellow led-blink"></div>
          <span class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-600">REGISTRATION</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <dl class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-6 gap-y-8">
        <div class="chivo-mono">
          <dt class="font-mono text-base text-led-blue flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="control-label">Date</span>
          </dt>
          <dd class="text-xl text-force-gray-800 font-kikai">2025/7/26(Sat) <span class="text-nowrap">9:30開場 9:45-18:00</span></dd>
        </div>
        <div class="chivo-mono">
          <dt class="font-mono text-base text-led-blue flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="control-label">Location</span>
          </dt>
          <dd class="text-xl text-led-yellow font-kikai">
            <a href="https://www.arc-net.or.jp/access/" class="text-nowrap underline hover:text-gray-600 transition-colors" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
              旭川リサーチセンター
            </a>
          </dd>
        </div>
        <div class="chivo-mono">
          <dt class="font-mono text-base text-led-blue flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="control-label">Venue</span>
          </dt>
          <dd class="text-xl text-force-gray-800 font-kikai">旭川リサーチセンター スタジオ</dd>
        </div>
        <div class="chivo-mono">
          <dt class="font-mono text-base text-led-blue flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="control-label">Price</span>
          </dt>
          <dd class="text-xl text-force-gray-800 font-kikai">有料 ※<span class="tape-correction">参加</span>種別ごとに金額が異なります</dd>
        </div>
      </dl>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
